item.title: CVE-2023-50423|2023-12-12T08:47:08.230Z -- sap_se -- sap-xssec
item.description: SAP BTP Security Services Integration Library ([Python] sap-xssec) - versions < 4.1.0, allow under certain conditions an escalation of privileges. On successful exploitation, an unauthenticated attacker can obtain arbitrary permissions within the application.
